615
00:40:33.640 --> 00:40:36.666
Wherever I end up in the
past. whatever "chapter" I'm in.

616
00:40:36.690 --> 00:40:41.996
I just draw the symbol on the paper

617
00:40:42.020 --> 00:40:43.586
and leave it there.

618
00:40:43.610 --> 00:40:45.546
If this works. when you pull me out.

619
00:40:45.570 --> 00:40:47.046
the symbol that I drew in the past

620
00:40:47.070 --> 00:40:49.110
will also be here on
the paper in the present.

621
00:40:54.790 --> 00:40:56.226
You've been waiting to do that

622
00:40:56.250 --> 00:40:57.766
